## **Best Practices for Asset Management**

### **1. Image Optimization**

```javascript
// Image optimization configuration
const imageConfig = {
  formats: ['webp', 'png', 'jpg'],
  sizes: [320, 640, 1024, 1920],
  quality: 85,
  lazyLoad: true
};

// Example usage
<img 
  src="assets/images/hero-bg.webp"
  srcset="
    assets/images/hero-320.webp 320w,
    assets/images/hero-640.webp 640w,
    assets/images/hero-1024.webp 1024w
  "
  loading="lazy"
  alt="Muqaddas Network Hero"
/>
```

### **2. CSS Variables**

```css
/* assets/styles/variables.css */
:root {
  /* Colors */
  --primary-color: #11998e;
  --secondary-color: #38ef7d;
  --charity-color: #f85149;
  --text-color: #ffffff;
  
  /* Spacing */
  --spacing-sm: 8px;
  --spacing-md: 16px;
  --spacing-lg: 24px;
  
  /* Typography */
  --font-primary: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  --font-size-base: 16px;
  --font-size-lg: 20px;
}
```

### **3. JavaScript Modules**

```javascript
// assets/scripts/modules/charity-counter.js
export class CharityCounter {
  constructor(elementId) {
    this.element = document.getElementById(elementId);
    this.count = 0;
  }
  
  async update() {
    const response = await fetch('/api/charity-stats');
    const data = await response.json();
    this.count = data.total;
    this.render();
  }
  
  render() {
    this.element.textContent = this.count.toLocaleString();
  }
}
```

### **4. Configuration Management**

```json
// assets/data/config.json
{
  "api": {
    "baseUrl": "https://api.muqaddasnetwork.com",
    "version": "v1",
    "timeout": 30000
  },
  "charity": {
    "profitShare": 0.45,
    "techDevelopment": 0.45,
    "familyEquity": 0.10
  },
  "features": {
    "liveCounter": true,
    "multiLanguage": true,
    "darkMode": true
  }
}
```

